## MEDIATION ANALYSIS
  
# But before we jump in too deep, I am going to start with the basics - 
# simply what is mediation analysis. Mediation analysis aims to examine
# the relationship between an exposure or a treatment and an outcome through
# a third variable called the mediator variable. The purpose of mediation
# analysis is to examine the causal relationships and to understand the
# underlying mechanisms, it's purpose is not to see how to build the best
